name: Odin
description: Odin is a dog who was mistaken for a Coyote and shot and now the "#JusticeForOdin" movement has started to roar on every single social media platform. The #JusticeForOdin movement which the end goal is "Odin's Law" - that every animal control officer and cop has to bear non-lethal in case of a similar situation, this is happening everywhere in the states and it's not the first case, but this can make a huge change! This is more than just a memecoin, this is a movement to support all pet owners to make a change in the real world and make it a safer place for our furry friends.
